content:
Participant Management

Reduce the time it takes to discover clinical trials by adding Criteria-Based Search and Filter (CBSF) to your Experience Cloud site. Quickly identify participants meeting clinical trial criteria using built-in OmniStudio components. Manage the complete enrollment journey efficiently with Stage Management.

Discover Clinical Trials Easily with Criteria-Based Search and Filter
Reduce the time it takes candidates to discover clinical trials by customizing a unified searchable field on your Experience Cloud site. Provide sorting options for search results displayed as cards and set up trial search targeting options based on location.

Evaluate Participant Eligibility With Prescreening Assessments
Swiftly identify participants who meet eligibility criteria for clinical trials using built-in Omnistudio components. Configure prescreening assessments to determine eligibility by responding to predefined questions. Encourage non-eligible candidates to share contact information for future trials.

Simplify Application Process With Built-in Templates
Enhance participant engagement and provide a seamless application process for eligible participants using built-in Omnistudio components. Capture essential participant details directly and self-paced without intermediaries.

Capture Informed Participant Consents with Flows
Eliminate complex paper-based processes by capturing candidate consent digitally. Customize the consent management process to meet business needs, support multiple languages, and comply with regulatory standards. Streamline consent version handling and capture timestamps for easier reporting.
title: Streamlining Clinical Trials with Participant Management
